  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wave-based, scorechasing old school arcade experience.<br></li><li>Your shields are powerful but limited. You need to defend and reflect from one side while tactically dodge from the other.<br></li><li>Choose between ramming enemy ships with your shield for a smaller score or go for broke by reflecting bullets back at them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.poster.avif?t=1687952101\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.webm?t=1687952101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.mp4?t=1687952101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Main graphics, programming and all of audio made by one developer, one-man band style (hope you like guitars).<br><br></li><li>A short but intense experience. I tried capturing the experience of playing a couple of rounds at the arcade before going to school.</li></ul><br><br>How high can you score? How long can you endure as the last line of defense?",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wave-based, scorechasing old school arcade experience.<br></li><li>Your shields are powerful but limited. You need to defend and reflect from one side while tactically dodge from the other.<br></li><li>Choose between ramming enemy ships with your shield for a smaller score or go for broke by reflecting bullets back at them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.poster.avif?t=1687952101\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.webm?t=1687952101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1517440/extras/ff9fd8848bc5f6d3d4c0f91c7cd1aca2.mp4?t=1687952101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Main graphics, programming and all of audio made by one developer, one-man band style (hope you like guitars).<br><br></li><li>A short but intense experience. I tried capturing the experience of playing a couple of rounds at the arcade before going to school.</li></ul><br><br>How high can you score? How long can you endure as the last line of defense?",
